Agent wants RB Salzburg star to shun biggest clubs. Manchester United’s aspirations of signing Erling Haaland are set to be blocked by the RB Salzburg’s striker Mino Raiola, The Athletic reports. READ ALSO:  CIES ranks second best after Messi The Italian, who is Paul Pogba’s agent, wants to prolific youngster to take another step before joining one of Europe’s biggest clubs.